<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About | Climate Solutions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  </head>

  <body data-theme="dark" class="min-h-screen bg-base-300 text-gray-200 flex flex-col">
 
    <header class="navbar bg-base-200 px-8 py-4 shadow-md">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Climate Solutions</a>
      </div>
      <nav>
        <ul class="menu menu-horizontal text-sm font-medium">
          <li><a href="/solutions/projects">View Projects</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="active text-green-400 font-semibold">About</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-12">
      <section class="max-w-5xl bg-base-200 p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-100 mb-6">About Me</h1>

        <p class="text-center text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Passionate developer & student exploring how technology and data can drive sustainable change.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            
            <img
              src="/images/seneca2.jpg"
              alt="Your Photo"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-80 h-80 object-cover border border-base-300"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-4">Hello! I’m Vedant Pandit</h2>
            <p>
              I’m currently pursuing <span class="font-semibold text-gray-100">Computer Programming</span> at
              <span class="text-green-400">Seneca Polytechnic</span> and enjoy building projects that combine clean design,
              functionality, and real-world purpose. This website showcases climate-related solutions I’ve studied and implemented
              as part of my coursework.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-4">
              Outside of coding, I love photography, fitness, and exploring sustainability ideas. I believe learning through
              practice and sharing knowledge with others helps growth — both as a developer and as a person.
            </p>

            <blockquote class="mt-6 text-gray-400 border-l-4 border-green-400 pl-4 italic">
              “Every line of code is a step toward a smarter, sustainable future.”
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    
    <footer class="bg-base-200 py-6 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm border-t border-base-300">
      <p>© 2025 Climate Solutions | Built with TailwindCSS & DaisyUI</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
